Key Match Events: Anrich Nortje took the first wicket
Steven Taylor dispatched his second ball for six and third for four to kick off the chase in imposing style
Rabada had caught at mid-wicket to end the 91-run partnership between Gous and Harmeet
Kagiso Rabada was pacy and accurate right from the get-go
Pre-Game Insights: USA have already automatically qualified for the 2026 tournament
Aiden Markram was South Africa's under-19 captain when they won the age-group World Cup 10 years ago and he may think his time has come
Post-Match Reflections: USA came really close, closer than the margin may suggest, and did not disgrace themselves at all
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the first time in the tournament that South Africa played on a batter-friendly pitch
The USA fielding was exceptional throughout the match
